name: Fire
description: Fire Rated flexible single core products for use in mains and sub-mains applications. Rated to 0.6/1kV, 110°C and WS52W, this LSOH range of Fire Rated cables are the only flexible single core power cable which does not require glass-mica tapes, thus reducing installation time and eliminating the need for respirators and special gloves.
benefits:
Unique polymer insulation hardens and protects in a fire
Easy to handle and install; no tapes to remove
Halogen free, low smoke, low toxic and corrosive emissions, flame retardant
misc: The Alsecure® Premium FRP cables are available in standard pair counts of 1, 2, 4, 6, 8, & 10, in conductor sizes 0.75mm2 and 1.5mm2.

Lift sub mains

name: Speaker
misc: When it comes to audio visual equipment, choosing the right cable is as important as choosing your theatre. The right connection will enhance image and sound quality, and allow your equipment to operate at its maximum potential. With an ever increasing amount of money being invested in screens and speakers, our range of cables is the vital link that can connect you with the home theatre quality you've dreamed of.
